title: Jimmy Carter National Historic Site: Blind / Low Vision
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Accessibility     Blind / Low Vision              Blind / Low Vision       All ranger programs strive to engage multiple senses and learning styles, and often include audio components. There are six (6) audio programs located in Plains High School, one (1) audio program at the Depot and nine (9) audio programs located at the Boyhood Farm.
